videoDetails.Title: The Best Panther In War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
Decal link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

The German tank tree in War Thunder has plenty of Panther tanks, but there's one that might be my favorite. The Panther F has a modernized turret and a rangefinder, making it much more aesthetically pleasing.
